Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

02:57.086 --> 02:58.306
Don't move!

04:18.285 --> 04:20.048
I can't run anymore.

04:26.576 --> 04:27.581
Please...

04:28.937 --> 04:30.229
don't hurt me.

04:34.220 --> 04:35.900
My head hurts.

04:38.386 --> 04:40.483
I want to talk to David.

04:45.165 --> 04:46.120
Please,

04:46.728 --> 04:48.742
let me talk to David Sandström...

05:03.468 --> 05:07.810
ReGenesis
4x01 <i>TB Or Not TB</i>

05:11.063 --> 05:14.150
Subtitles
Team NorBAC

